Hey, what are you doing, Sue?

Hehe, I figure that I should probably make my moves

Hmm, I won!

Oh, you are really a big help!
That monster caused us lots of troubles.

You are a young and veteran warrior, good for you!
And the weapon you are using, I've never seen it... Marvelous.

Uh, warrior? No, I am an alchemist!
My goal is to make my atelier No. 1 in the kingdom...

Puff... Congratulations, warrior.

That's enough, I quit! I'll not kill monsters in this world!
I got to come up with another idea...

Hmm...
It's not easy to become No. 1 in the kingdom...
